oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Jeannie C. Riley at Perkins High School Gym
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Riley, Jeannie C.; Metal photoplates;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (red and black on white) announcing the Sounds of Nashville with Jeannie C. Riley and Red River Symphony, Guy Shannon, Ural Albert, and Johnny Strumn at the Perkins High School Gym on May 17. Poster features metal photoplates of Jeannie C. Riley, Guy Shannon, and Ural Albert. Poster was printed for job no. 16214. For additional information about this poster see https://digi.countrymusichalloffame.org/digital/collection/hatch3/id/24065.
